 1ï¸âƒ£ NIC (Network Interface Card)

 ğŸ”¹ What is NIC?

NIC ek network card hota hai jo kisi machine ko network se connect karta hai.

ğŸ“Œ Real Life Example:
Mobile ka SIM card ğŸ“±
SIM nahi â†’ network nahi

 ğŸ”¹ NIC Portable hoti hai

