 2ï¸âƒ£ Network Switch

 ğŸ”¹ What is Network Switch?

Network switch ka kaam hota hai:

 Multiple devices ko same network ke andar connect karna
 Data sirf correct device tak bhejna

ğŸ“Œ Use case:
Office / Data Center / Cloud network

 ğŸ”¹ Large Network me Role

 Large networks ko efficiently manage karta hai
 Fast & intelligent hota hai
 MAC address ke basis par kaam karta hai

---

 3ï¸âƒ£ Hub vs Switch

| Hub                   | Switch                |
| --------------------- | --------------------- |
| Data sabko bhejta hai | Sirf target device ko |
| Slow                  | Fast                  |
| Intelligent nahi      | Intelligent           |
| Old technology        | Modern technology     |

ğŸ“Œ AWS me Hub use nahi hota
AWS internally virtual switches use karta hai

---

 4ï¸âƒ£ Network Switch (In Detail â€“ AWS Perspective)

 AWS me switch directly visible nahi hota
 AWS automatically networking handle karta hai
 Same subnet ke andar communication switch ke through hota hai

ğŸ“Œ Conclusion:
Tum AWS me switch configure nahi karte, AWS khud manage karta hai

