 6ï¸âƒ£ Firewall

Firewall ka kaam hota hai network security provide karna.

 ğŸ” AWS me Firewall Types

 ğŸ”¹ Security Group

 EC2 level firewall
 Stateful
 Sirf allow rules

 ğŸ”¹ Network ACL (NACL)

 Subnet level firewall
 Stateless
 Allow + Deny rules

 ğŸ”¹ WAF

 Web Application Firewall
 SQL Injection, XSS attacks se protection

