 8ï¸âƒ£ Elastic Network Interface (ENI)

 ğŸ”¹ What is ENI?

ENI = AWS ka virtual NIC

 ğŸ”¹ ENI ke Components

 Private IP
 Public IP (optional)
 MAC Address
 Security Group

 ğŸ”¥ Important Point

> ENI portable hoti hai
> Ek EC2 se detach karke dusri EC2 me attach kar sakte ho

ğŸ“Œ Use Case:
Failover, troubleshooting, high availability

