 ğŸ”¥ Final Summary (Quick Revision)

 NIC = Network card
 ENI = AWS NIC
 Switch = Same network communication
 Router = Different network connection
 Firewall = Security
 Routing Table = Traffic direction
 VPC = Private AWS network

